END QUOTE 

MAY 

CAUSED A BLACKOUT OF MOST OF LIMA AT A TIME WHEN 
THE POPE WAS VISITING. 

APRIL 

HANGED THREE PEASANT WOMEN IN THE HIGHLANDS NEAR 
