THE GCC FOREIGN MINISTERS WILL DEPART CAIRO TOMORROW AND 
TRAVEL TO JEDDAH, WHERE THEY WILL ISSUE A STRONG 
STATEMENT AGAINST IRAQ.  RIYADH 6070 
 
