TO QADHAFI, WE MAY SUGGEST TO HIM THAT THE RECORD OF ALL 
COMMUNICATIONS BETWEEN THE SECRETARIAT AND THE LIBYAN 
GOVERNMENT ON PA 103 BE CIRCULATED AS SECURITY COUNCIL 
DOCUMENTS. 
 
 
