DEPARTMENT INTERNET AND INTRANET SITES. THE INTERNET 
SITE ADDRESS IS: 
WWW.STATE.GOV/WWW/PERDIEMS/ALLOWANCES(UNDERSC ORE) 
INDEX.HTML. THE INTRANET SITE (INTERNAL STATE 
DEPARTMENT SITE) ADDRESS IS: 
HTTP://AOPRALS.A.STATE.GOV/. 
 
